meta.expressionLhs: ROUND_MONTH ( PU_FIRST ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."EVENTTIME" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Order Item' ) ) AS "#{\"EKKO\".\"AEDAT\"}" FORMAT "%Y-%m"

buttons.variableValue: CASE WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") >= 0 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 THEN 'a) 0 - 100 <%=currency_symbol%>' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 100 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500 THEN 'b) 100 - 500 <%=currency_symbol%>' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 500 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 1500 THEN 'c) 500 - 1.500 <%=currency_symbol%>'  WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 1500 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 5000 THEN 'd) 1.500 - 5.000 <%=currency_symbol%>'  WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 5000 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 10000 THEN 'd) 5.000 - 10.000 <%=currency_symbol%>'  ELSE 'e) > 10.000 <%=currency_symbol%>' END

variables.title: Dimensionbutton_Overview
variables.variableValue:
CASE WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") >= 0 
AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 
THEN 'a) 0 - 100 <%=currency_symbol%>'  
WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 100
AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500 
THEN 'b) 100 - 500 <%=currency_symbol%>'  
WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 500 
AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 1000 
THEN 'c) 500 - 1.000 <%=currency_symbol%>'  
WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 1000 
AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 10000 
THEN 'd) 1.000 - 10.000 <%=currency_symbol%>' 
ELSE 'e) > 10.000 <%=currency_symbol%>' END

variables.title: Dimensionbutton_Overview
variables.variableValue: CASE WHEN ISNULL(LFA1.VBUND)=1 THEN 'External' ELSE 'Internal' END

variables.name: Three_way_match_filter
variables.value:
Filter PROCESS EQUALS 'Record Goods Receipt';
Filter PROCESS EQUALS 'Record Invoice Receipt';

variables.name: filter7
variables.value:
CASE WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."LOEKZ") = 1 THEN 'not deleted'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'S' THEN 'locked'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'L' THEN 'deleted'
     ELSE "EKPO"."LOEKZ"
END

variables.name: filter6
variables.value:
CASE
    WHEN ISNULL("LFA1"."VBUND") = 1 THEN 'External'
    ELSE 'Internal'
END

variables.name: rework_activities
variables.value: 'Block Purchase Order Item','Cancel Goods Receipt','Cancel Invoice Receipt','Delete Purchase Order Item','Remove Payment Block','Set Payment Block'

variables.name: change_activities
variables.value: 'Change Currency','Change Delivery Indicator','Change Final Invoice Indicator','Change Price','Change Quantity','Change Storage Location','Change Vendor'

variables.name: B_KPI
variables.value: AVG( CASE          WHEN ISNULL(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>) = 1 THEN NULL         WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 AND DAYS_BETWEEN(TODAY(),<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>) >= 0 THEN 1.0         WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 THEN 0.0         WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>, <%= GR_VARIABLE %>) <= 0         AND  DAYS_BETWEEN(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>, <%= GR_VARIABLE %>) >= -3     THEN 1.0      ELSE 0.0      END )
